siteMetadata.title: I'm Annie Liu
siteMetadata.description: Hi! I'm Annie Liu (she/her/hers), a second year undergrad at MIT pursuing a major in computer science. I'm extremely interested in how technology can tell us more about ourselves and better inform the decisions we make in our lives. I love completing projects and learning new things along the way! Other than coding, I enjoy writing, running, rock climbing, and listening to music.
siteMetadata.author: Annie Liu
